<i>adverb</i>: 측은히 [츠근히], 가엾이 [가ː엽씨] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>측은히 [츠근히]</dt><br>
<dd>sympathetically; compassionately</dd><br>
<dd>가엾고 불쌍하게.</dd><br>
<dd>With sympathy and compassion.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>가엾이 [가ː엽씨]</dt><br>
<dd>compassionately</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 아플 정도로 불쌍하고 딱하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a compassionate way that feels pity for another.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>